profile:
We specialize in:
Staging Houses for Selling, ReDesigning Homes for Living.
Staging - makes your house more competive, memorable, showable and photographable in today's selling market.
ReDesign - going Green!  We use what you already own to create rooms with a Wow factor.  Rooms that you'll love coming home to.
Member of the Canadian ReDesigners & Stagers Association.
R.E.S.A.
We support Ovarian Cancer Canada
hours: we work in your home/house - no store front
